go to allure site - https://allurereport.org/docs/install-for-windows/
open scoop website- https://scoop.sh/
Open Windows Powershell
Run following commands:
Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser
Invoke-RestMethod -Uri https://get.scoop.sh | Invoke-Expression
Then run command to install allure - scoop install allure
Add dependency in the project: we are using TestNG so add TestNG dependency. Review the Allure website
use this link - https://allurereport.org/docs/testng/
